{"tid":1975093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家係幾時開始變成而家既政見","createTime":"2020-04-16T09:50:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T11:48:23.000Z","uid":128261,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"405b7804fd5174db174ae614adb949407bdb2a30","tid":1975093,"uid":128261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T09:50:40.000Z","msg":"小弟2010年仲係和理非大中華膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係2012年開始既中港矛盾令我變成本土派<br />\n睇住街上面充斥住蝗蟲大媽水貨狗，鋪頭慢慢變曬做金鋪藥房<br />\n令我心知必須本土優先，反對中港融合，要同中國人一刀兩斷<br />\n後來既雨革、魚革同今次反送中運動，只係強化左我既睇法<br />\n唔知大家又係點，特別係後生啲既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ba19e40ea0f4a7f00b4b519fc4e0cb18b6340e9","tid":1975093,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T09:51:38.000Z","msg":"同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81db91fe2527f37a6f456f0448d969c229614bc7","tid":1975093,"uid":249794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T09:52:24.000Z","msg":"雨傘中期<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fca4bd276790d062bcca38be2949e7f9eb2cba42","tid":1975093,"uid":245065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T09:52:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"679b5338138ad801f7a1b00b170438c78b3645ab","tid":1975093,"uid":299311,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T09:53:13.000Z","msg":"無 以前見到啲08奧運吉祥物已經覺得好核突 成浸支那除"},{"pid":"de13728fa8a3ddea956263d4f415a3c6cfc2f1cb","tid":1975093,"uid":325346,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T09:53:58.000Z","msg":"2012投范國威<br />\n港人優先<br />\n<br />\n2016投天琦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71a7495401eb46c7504f3ca30fa1da9a1db53a76","tid":1975093,"uid":6604,"like"